センチメンタルな恋
A sentimental love

40
00:06:33,008 --> 00:06:37,008
突き進むなら 二人で
If we are to push forward, let's do it together

41
00:06:37,508 --> 00:06:43,508
革命道中 だって夢に熱中
On our journey of revolution, because we're obsessed with our dream

42
00:06:44,008 --> 00:06:46,808
ダメダメ！ 待て待て！
No, no! Wait, wait!

43
00:06:46,808 --> 00:06:49,008
呪いも病も抱きしめたい
I want to embrace even curses and illnesses

44
