94
00:10:56,516 --> 00:10:59,016
心臓がカウントしてる
...my heart is counting it down.

95
00:10:59,016 --> 00:11:04,016
叶えても 叶えても
Even if they're granted, even if they come true,

96
00:11:04,016 --> 00:11:08,516
終わらない願い
