Did you guys notice things like Turbo Watamate?

138
00:14:40,516 --> 00:14:44,016
ぜひ細かいところまで観てもらえると嬉しいです！
I hope you look closely at all the little details!

139
00:14:44,016 --> 00:14:48,016
ここからはゲストパートもあります！
From here, we have the guest performances too!

140
00:14:48,016 --> 00:14:52,016
みんなの好きなアニソンも出てくるかも？
Maybe your favorite anisong will be performed?

141
00:14:52,016 --> 00:14:57,016
ということで、ゲストパート、盛り上がっていきましょう！
So, let's get hyped up for the guest part!

142
00:15:24,924 --> 00:15:31,924
割れた鏡の中 映る君の姿
Your reflection in the broken mirror...

143
00:15:32,324 --> 00:15:36,124
泣いている 泣いている
is crying, is crying...

144
00:15:36,524 --> 00:15:40,024
細い月をなぞる指
Fingers tracing the crescent moon.

145
00:15:40,824 --> 00:15:47,824
誰を呼んでいるの 消えた恋の背中
Who are you calling out to? The back of a faded love...

146
00:15:48,124 --> 00:15:52,224
何度でも 何度でも
Again and again, again and again,

147
00:15:52,524 --> 00:15:56,024
君の窓を叩くから
Because I'll keep knocking on your window.

148
00:15:56,424 --> 00:16:00,424
夜の加速度に 背中押されて
Pushed forward by the acceleration of the night,

149
00:16:03,424 --> 00:16:05,624
糸が切れる様に
as if the thread is about to snap...

150
00:16:07,124 --> 00:16:11,524
ただ、君を 君を強く
I was simply holding you, holding you...

151
00:16:12,024 --> 00:16:15,524
抱いてた
so tightly.

152
00:16:16,224 --> 00:16:20,224
アンバランスなKissを交わして
Let's share an unbalanced kiss

153
00:16:20,224 --> 00:16:24,024
愛に近づけよ
and draw closer to love.

154
00:16:24,224 --> 00:16:28,024
君の涙も 哀しい嘘も
May your tears, and your sad lies too,

155
00:16:28,224 --> 00:16:31,524
僕の心に
rest...

156
00:16:31,624 --> 00:16:35,524
眠れ
...in my heart.

157
00:16:41,024 --> 00:16:48,024
昨日へのMerry-go-round 君を運んでゆく
The merry-go-round to yesterday carries you away.

158
00:16:48,124 --> 00:16:52,224
止めたくて 止めたくて
Desperately wanting to stop it, to stop it,

159
00:16:52,324 --> 00:16:56,024
僕は鍵を探してる
I am searching for the key.

160
00:16:56,224 --> 00:17:00,024
崩れ落ちそうな 空を支えて
Supporting a sky that seems about to collapse,

